A rally in support of the Citizenship Amendment Act (CAA) turned violent in Madhya Pradesh‚Äôs Rajgarh district on Sunday, with the participants attacking the police after the latter used force against them.

According to the police, permission was not granted for the rally and Section 144 was in place in the area.

